130
00:14:07,740 --> 00:14:10,330
SPEAKER_20: The game's not over yet!

140
00:14:44,779 --> 00:14:47,769
SPEAKER_20: I am very sorry, but you've got nothing left.

141
00:14:48,049 --> 00:14:51,779
SPEAKER_20: What could you stake the bet on?
We don't accept empty bets.

146
00:15:03,730 --> 00:15:06,529
SPEAKER_20: We'll formalize the transfer in a few days...

147
00:15:06,600 --> 00:15:08,289
SPEAKER_20: and explain to your old man.

163
00:17:30,210 --> 00:17:32,400
SPEAKER_20: Mr. Xu, any mistakes?

289
00:32:42,920 --> 00:32:45,220
SPEAKER_20: The wounded who froze to death.

313
00:34:31,230 --> 00:34:32,460
SPEAKER_20: So, no running?

501
00:58:25,789 --> 00:58:27,420
SPEAKER_20: This is too much.

569
01:05:52,960 --> 01:05:55,360
SPEAKER_20: Youqing, is that tea for me?

813
01:31:06,489 --> 01:31:08,079
SPEAKER_20: Aren't you busy!

814
01:31:08,659 --> 01:31:10,680
SPEAKER_20: I brought some colleagues.

820
01:31:29,710 --> 01:31:32,510
SPEAKER_20: You're just in time. We've just finished.

822
01:31:36,520 --> 01:31:38,449
SPEAKER_20: We must be going.

829
01:32:01,979 --> 01:32:04,810
SPEAKER_20: Thanks, we'll go to the factory bathhouse.

863
01:36:16,430 --> 01:36:17,989
SPEAKER_20: Chairman Mao...

864
01:36:18,869 --> 01:36:21,600
SPEAKER_20: Comrade Fengxia's mine now.

897
01:40:04,689 --> 01:40:06,279
SPEAKER_20: Dad! Mom!

898
01:40:13,100 --> 01:40:14,470
SPEAKER_20: Come on in!

912
01:41:22,140 --> 01:41:23,329
SPEAKER_20: Really?

913
01:41:23,939 --> 01:41:28,000
SPEAKER_20: I just came from the hospital.
The doctor says it's due in autumn.

916
01:41:37,489 --> 01:41:38,680
SPEAKER_20: Cheers!

944
01:43:25,989 --> 01:43:28,829
SPEAKER_20: He's been arrested as a capitalist.

945
01:43:29,000 --> 01:43:31,829
SPEAKER_20: They held a public trial against him.

946
01:43:32,069 --> 01:43:34,930
SPEAKER_20: We have to draw a line between us and him.

1011
01:48:44,340 --> 01:48:46,899
SPEAKER_20: - But you won't stay?
- No, thanks.

1012
01:48:57,359 --> 01:49:00,090
SPEAKER_20: Never mind. Let's go. Don't worry.

1042
01:50:52,210 --> 01:50:54,829
SPEAKER_20: Do as Mommy says and push.

1043
01:50:54,909 --> 01:50:56,640
SPEAKER_20: Everything will be fine.

1078
01:53:31,029 --> 01:53:33,159
SPEAKER_20: We dragged him here today...

1079
01:53:33,300 --> 01:53:36,270
SPEAKER_20: to educate him, to criticize him...

1080
01:53:37,340 --> 01:53:39,899
SPEAKER_20: and to let him witness her giving birth.

1086
01:54:03,300 --> 01:54:05,289
SPEAKER_20: That's professor Wang...

1087
01:54:05,500 --> 01:54:07,229
SPEAKER_20: head of obstetrics.

1149
01:59:09,670 --> 01:59:11,329
SPEAKER_20: Are they in there?

1158
01:59:35,359 --> 01:59:37,689
SPEAKER_20: Erxi, you're a lucky man!

1159
01:59:37,760 --> 01:59:40,890
SPEAKER_20: My son was only 5.5 pounds.

1161
01:59:43,239 --> 01:59:45,760
SPEAKER_20: If you get a car from the factory...

1162
01:59:45,840 --> 01:59:48,399
SPEAKER_20: we can drive Fengxia home.

1171
02:00:25,310 --> 02:00:28,539
SPEAKER_20: You two get the car, we'll be fine.

1183
02:01:44,920 --> 02:01:47,090
SPEAKER_20: Wouldn't Dr. Wang know?

1253
02:07:11,979 --> 02:07:13,350
SPEAKER_20: It's okay.

1254
02:07:16,119 --> 02:07:18,590
SPEAKER_20: We shouldn't have given him water.

1262
02:07:42,550 --> 02:07:44,180
SPEAKER_20: Not just buns...

1263
02:07:44,279 --> 02:07:46,310
SPEAKER_20: anything made from wheat.

